SHANGRI-LA FRONTIER 2. SEZON

01:30.430 --> 01:31.530
#46: WOLFGANG DENİZİ TERK EDİYOR

01:31.530 --> 01:32.990
#46: WOLFGANG DENİZİ TERK EDİYOR  
